{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6ec50ac004","title":"复班禅额尔德尼电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9974559df3","index":0,"year":1957,"month":3,"day":6,"articleId":"6ec50ac004"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"76194f550c","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6ec50ac004","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"班禅额尔德尼，即班禅额尔德尼·确吉坚赞，西藏宗教领袖之一，当时任政协全国委员会副主席、西藏自治区筹备委员会第一副主任委员。"},{"id":"ba6958f3e5","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6ec50ac004","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"火鸡年，藏历纪年。藏历采用干支纪年，以“阴、阳”与“木、火、土、金、水”五行相配代替十干，以十二生肖（鼠、牛、虎、免、龙、蛇、马、羊、猴、鸡、狗、猪）代替十二支，再以十干和十二支相配，如阳木鼠年、阴木牛年等。以此计算，1957年是藏历阴火鸡年，也称火鸡年。"},{"id":"6e47614e6c","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6ec50ac004","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"达赖喇嘛，即达赖喇嘛·丹增嘉措，西藏宗教领袖之一，当时任全国人大常委会副委员长、西藏自治区筹备委员会主任委员。"},{"id":"2a37e16bd7","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6ec50ac004","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"释迎车尼，古印度释迎族人，佛教创始人。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2fbac38d20","type":"title","text":"复班禅额尔德尼叫电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6ec50ac004"},{"id":"76194f550c","type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的班禅额尔德尼","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6ec50ac004"},{"id":"ba6958f3e5","type":"paragraph","text":"你从印度回到日喀则时给我拍来的电报和火鸡年元旦给我的贺电，我都收到了，谢谢你的祝贺。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6ec50ac004"},{"id":"6e47614e6c","type":"paragraph","text":"这次你和达赖喇嘛去印度参加释迎军尼湿聚二千五百年纪念会，在加强中印友谊方面做出了有益的贡献。祝你在新的一年内在西藏地区各项工作上取得新的成就，祝你身体健康。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6ec50ac004"},{"id":"2a37e16bd7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6ec50ac004"},{"id":"7fff06469a","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五七年三月六日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6ec50ac004"}],"page":{"id":"8bc6cd12ef","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6ec50ac004","start":355,"end":355}}}},"__N_SSG":true}